Description:
Simply Stunning!
Have you been looking for a reasonably priced home that represents fantastic value with no renovation needed? This could be for you!
This beautifully kept home will be a pleasure to come home to after a hard days work and offers an array of features including; a modern laminate kitchen with plenty of bench/cupboard space, easy to clean timber look flooring throughout and 2 large bedrooms both with built in robes which are comfortably accommodating. The bathroom sparkles and is luxuriously appointed while the separate laundry has convenient access to the manicured rear garden". The lounge is ample in size with enough room for larger sofas and car accommodation is supplied with a separately titled carport at the rear of the block.
The location is fantastic within walking distance to local shops, Dandenong High School & Dandenong North Primary Schools, Dandenong Hospital and the local Market.
Raise the curtain on a new lifestyle today.call now.

Description:
Beautifully Appointed and Brilliantly Located
Nested in the stylish and vibrant metro village estate triple storey town home the perfect location for young families, investors or professionals. Located in such a prime pocket, tucked away in this serene complex, enter via the leafy private street or securely through the single lock up garage. This absolute delight comprises of two bedrooms on the top floor with a two-way bathroom, an open plan middle level with kitchen, meals, living and balcony plus on the ground floor is a study nook/office space.
This townhouse with almost all amenities including nearby park & playground, short stroll to the train station & bus stops, Dandenong plaza, cafes & easy access to freeways. Split system cooling & heating through the house, stainless steel appliances including gas cooktop and dishwasher. Extras include the single lock up garage with secure access, multiple heaters throughout, downlights and more. For your chance to own this triple storey treat, call me today!
A flat block in a great locationa combination that shouldn't be missed!

PLEASE NOTE: Due to the ongoing COVID-19 situation, we will only be conducting private inspections for this property. Please contact your agent to arrange an inspection. Thank you for your understanding.
A vision of style and sophistication, this quality townhouse is firmly focused on easy family living with its dual living zones and low-maintenance courtyard, while its quiet court setting grants easy access to amenities. Zoned for family harmony, the home opens to reveal a spacious lounge room and adjacent dining zone that's adorned with square set ceilings and sleek floorboards underfoot. Continuing through to the rear of the home, an open plan kitchen and meals/family room relishes stainless steel appliances including dishwasher plus a breakfast bench, with sliding doors enticing you out to the delightful courtyard. Positioned for peace and privacy, all three robed bedroom rest on the upper level and are comforted by carpet, whereas the master bedroom delights in direct ensuite effect access to the family bathroom with separate toilet. Further complemented by a 2nd downstairs bathroom with toilet, laundry, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, water tank, garden shed plus a single garage with internal access. Conveniently placed within close proximity to Chisholm Institute, schools, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong Plaza, transport, reserves plus Monash and EastLink Freeways.
Photo ID required at all inspections.

Description:
Low Maintenance Lifestyle and Excellance
From the moment you enter this 3-bedroom townhouse you will be captivated. Ideal for the first homeowner, young family or those looking to enjoy a low maintenance property this quality home is sure to impress.
Features include:
Main bedroom on ground floor with WIR and Ensuite
Upstairs 2 Bedrooms with BIRs serviced by central bathroom
Formal lounge room and separate dining
Undercover alfresco, ideal for the home entertainer
Huge double remote garage with secure internal access via private courtyard
Ducted Heating
Split System Air Conditioning
Perfectly positioned amongst pre primary, primary and secondary schools, walking distance to local shops and park, along with easy access to Dandenong Plaza and Market, Hospitals, Princess Highway, Eastlink, Monash Freeway, trains, buses and bike trails.
Call Tony now on (03) 9568 8000 to arrange your private inspection.

Description:
PRIME DEVELOPMENT OPPORTUNITY IN PREMIUM LOCATION
Situated in a brilliant and central pocket of the most sought-after Dandenong locale this magnificent allotment (730m2 approx) is ready for you!
It definitely has the potential with some rejuvenation to be liveable although long term the true value lies within the land it sits upon.
Opportunity abounds for the lucky buyer to redevelop this level rectangular site, whether it be with 3 dwellings, two homes or a dream home (all stca).
Positioned in a quiet street yet within very short walking distance of quality local schools including St Johns Secondary, St Mary"s and Dandenong Primary Schools with the Dandenong Plaza, all central facilities and parklands right nearby.
Don't miss out for this fabulous opportunity in a Brilliant Location!

Description:
Apartment Living In Style
An edgy new look has come to Dandenong in this bespoke new 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom corner ground floor apartment. Beautifully designed to capture an urban designer feel with custom cabinetry that maximises the space.
This quality-built abode features a vogue gallery-style kitchen with stone bench tops, pantry, north face living & dining opening to an alfresco. On offer there is also a stunning main bedroom (BIR & sleek ensuite) and double bedroom (BIR) along with European laundry and glamorous bathroom.
With a variety of great restaurants and shops sitting at your door, there's so much to love about the cosmopolitan feel and lifestyle that surrounds you, with Dandenong station and buses to get you where you need.
*** WHEN INSPECTING THE PROPERTY, PLEASE MEET OUTSIDE THE PROPERTY FACING HORNSBY STREET ***
Amenities nearby:
Dandenong Train Station
Accounting & Taxation Services
Automotive Mechanics (including Sheen Panel, Dandy Exhausts & DEA Performance)
Fish World Aquarium/Priority Pets
Doherty's Dandenong 24/7 Gym
Quick access to the M1 Freeway
Drum Theatre on Langhorne Street
Parkmore Shopping Centre & Dandenong Shopping Centre
Chisholm TAFE, Dandenong Library, Dandenong South Primary School & St Mary's Primary School
